{{Quote|Should I ask how you got this information?''"<br />"''You didn't hire us to calm tempers with jeru tea and sweetcakes.|[[Natasi Daala]] and [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]], regarding the [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorians']] uncovering of the [[Lecersen Conspiracy]]|<ref name="Ascension">''[[Fate of the Jedi: Ascension]]''</ref>}}
'''Jeru tea''' was [[Callista Ming]]'s favorite [[Tea/Legends|drink]]. It was sweet with a syrup-like texture and had a calming effect on the drinker.<ref name="Darksaber">[[Darksaber (novel)|''Darksaber'']]</ref>

